    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel temporary. like, it feels more like reality. everyone says it gets better, but that's just something people say so they don't have to deal with the truth. the truth is that there's nothing out there. no purpose, no meaning, just entropy. if everything is just going to end in nothing anyway, why am i even struggling to keep going?",
